				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/H%E1%BB%8Dc-d%E1%BB%8Bch-k%E1%BB%B3/poem-g3ZO1UtxAPeDnpU-U9Hbtg">Học dịch kỳ - 學奕棋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%95-Nha-h%C3%A0nh/poem-36cUFRpE0tTblo4fRKpVmQ">Hổ Nha hành - 虎牙行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/Minh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-gia-hu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-3aa2tlihTrwlAHWnLopSow">Minh Đạo gia huấn - 明道家訓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Phong-t%E1%BA%ADt-chu-trung-ph%E1%BB%A5c-ch%E1%BA%A9m-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%93-Nam-th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-maRxAMOCboIbSdvxXl781Q">Phong tật chu trung phục chẩm thư hoài tam thập lục vận, phụng trình Hồ Nam thân hữu - 風疾舟中伏枕書懷三十六韻，奉呈湖南親友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-ki%E1%BB%81u-ti%C3%AAn-%C4%90i%E1%BA%BFu-%C4%91%C3%A0i/poem-2yzXyHJUmXU_0XKOwM--LA">Thước kiều tiên - Điếu đài - 鵲橋仙－釣臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-M%C3%B4n-ph%C3%BA/poem-NExLx3ZnSypitVJgFbFpOA">Trường Môn phú - 長門賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/author-HC1oHxsir20vL_KcVXiEhQ">Tư Mã Tương Như</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-xu%C3%A2n-du/poem-Vd-sLUx85IwQfGg99nkarw">Tương Châu xuân du - 襄州春遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/author-YaU63-B8n1CAEl8OjKg7AQ">Bì Nhật Hưu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%A0-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Tỳ bà hành - 琵琶行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Uy%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%93-kh%C3%BAc/poem-aw_k9y8xFFL9IBn8k3lN1A">Uyên hồ khúc - 鴛湖曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Vi%C3%AAn-Vi%C3%AAn-kh%C3%BAc/poem-33CduH4NfT9ibV757snSEw">Viên Viên khúc - 圓圓曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br></div>	</div>
